title: Superman - Panic in the Sky
description:
This torrent includes one of the best of the Superman title cross-over stories from 1992: Panic in the Sky.

This is not the classic episode of the George Reeves Superman series by the same name ;)

The main villain is Brainiac (the 1990&#039;s version with the Snydely Whiplash moustache) and the heroes included Superman, Justice League, Supergirl, Orion of The New Gods, et. al.

I could give you a whole lot of other Superman trivia to provide context, but all in all, this is a good read and worthy of becoming a torrent in its own right.

Thanks to the scanners and the original sources.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
